### Blockers
 -  None.

##  Outcome
 -  *LANDED `f20e2ec7`* (2026-06-16): audited io/utf8/main.cpp — no remaining
    live `JSStringRef` leaks (all paired w/ release; the cited utf8:18 was JS-003,
    convert.cpp is dead); wrapped both poll callbacks (`timeout_cb`,
    `JABCioNetOnEvent`) in `try{}catch(...){}` + a single-thread re-entrancy guard
    (`JABCioReentry`). C++-throw containment verified RED (abort) → GREEN via a new
    `jabc_test` row.

